ce:section.ce:para:
Lanthanum-incorporated carbon dots (C-dots:La) were synthesized, and a nanocomposite (NC) of β-Cyclodextrin-polyethylene glycol-folate (CD-PEG-fol) with them was made (Scheme 1
                        ). It was characterized by XRD (Fig. 1
                        A). The broadband indicates mostly amorphous NC. Moreover, a characteristic peak is observed at 19° (2θ), about the (002) reflection plane, illustrative of C-dots.
